---
import Container from "~/components/widgets/Container.astro";
---

<div id="problem-solution" class="bg-gray-50 py-16 dark:bg-gray-900">
  <Container>
    <!-- Section Title and Description -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-5xl text-center">
        The Problem We Solve
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center leading-relaxed">
        Businesses worldwide face immense challenges in ensuring compliance with evolving regulations while protecting themselves from financial crimes like money laundering. Traditional methods are often ineffective and time-consuming, exposing companies to substantial risk.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards Section -->
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 justify-items-center">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8 dark:bg-gray-800 transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-red-500/50">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-16 h-16 text-red-500 dark:text-red-300 mb-6">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4a8 8 0 11-8 8 8.01 8.01 0 018-8zm0 14a6 6 0 100-12 6 6 0 000 12z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">
          Inefficient Compliance Processes
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
          Manual compliance efforts are slow, prone to errors, and unable to keep up with the fast-paced regulatory landscape.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8 dark:bg-gray-800 transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-orange-500/50">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-16 h-16 text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-300 mb-6">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4a8 8 0 11-8 8 8.01 8.01 0 018-8zm0 14a6 6 0 100-12 6 6 0 000 12z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">
          Increased Fraud Risks
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
          The lack of advanced AI-powered monitoring systems allows illicit activities to go unnoticed, increasing the risk of fraud.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8 dark:bg-gray-800 transition-all hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/50">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-16 h-16 text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-300 mb-6">
          <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 4a8 8 0 11-8 8 8.01 8.01 0 018-8zm0 14a6 6 0 100-12 6 6 0 000 12z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
        </svg>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">
          Manual Risk Assessments
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center leading-relaxed">
          Companies often rely on outdated systems for risk assessments, leading to inefficient, time-consuming, and costly processes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>

<style>
  /* Global Styles */
  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  }

  /* Title and Description */
  .text-center .text-4xl {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .text-center p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.75rem;
    color: #4b5563;
  }

  /* Cards Layout */
  .grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); /* Auto adjust based on screen size */
    justify-items: center;
  }

  /* Card Styling */
  .flex {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .flex .w-16 {
    width: 4rem;
    height: 4rem;
  }

  .card {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Dark Mode Styling */
  .dark .bg-gray-50 {
    background-color: #1f2937; /* Dark background */
  }

  .dark .card {
    background-color: #2d3748;
  }

  .dark .card h3 {
    color: #edf2f7;
  }

  .dark .card p {
    color: #cbd5e0;
  }

  .dark .card svg {
    color: #facc15;
  }
</style>
